select * from `users` where `id` = 24 limit 1

select `tbl_department`.*, `tbl_user_type_detail`.`user_id` as `pivot_user_id`, `tbl_user_type_detail`.`department_id` as `pivot_department_id`, `tbl_user_type_detail`.`user_type_id` as `pivot_user_type_id`, `tbl_user_type_detail`.`start_date` as `pivot_start_date`, `tbl_user_type_detail`.`end_date` as `pivot_end_date`, `tbl_user_type_detail`.`status` as `pivot_status`, `tbl_user_type_detail`.`created_at` as `pivot_created_at`, `tbl_user_type_detail`.`updated_at` as `pivot_updated_at` from `tbl_department` inner join `tbl_user_type_detail` on `tbl_department`.`id` = `tbl_user_type_detail`.`department_id` where `tbl_user_type_detail`.`user_id` = 24
select count(*) as aggregate from `tbl_roles` inner join `tbl_user_roles` on `tbl_roles`.`id` = `tbl_user_roles`.`role_id` where `tbl_user_roles`.`user_id` = 24 and `role_name` = 'admin'

select `tbl_lead`.`lead_id`, `color_code`, (CASE
WHEN tbl_lead.main_lead = "KOL" THEN CONCAT("KOL: ", tbl_lead.sub_lead)
WHEN tbl_lead.main_lead = "External Edufair" THEN CONCAT("External Edufair: ", tbl_eduf_lead.title)
WHEN tbl_lead.main_lead = "All-In Event" THEN CONCAT("All-In Event: ", tbl_events.event_title)
ELSE tbl_lead.main_lead
END) AS lead_source, COUNT((CASE
WHEN tbl_lead.main_lead = "KOL" THEN CONCAT("KOL: ", tbl_lead.sub_lead)
WHEN tbl_lead.main_lead = "External Edufair" THEN CONCAT("External Edufair: ", tbl_eduf_lead.title)
WHEN tbl_lead.main_lead = "All-In Event" THEN CONCAT("All-In Event: ", tbl_events.event_title)
ELSE tbl_lead.main_lead
END)) AS lead_source_count from `tbl_client_prog` left join `tbl_client` on `tbl_client`.`id` = `tbl_client_prog`.`client_id` left join `tbl_lead` on `tbl_lead`.`lead_id` = `tbl_client`.`lead_id` left join `tbl_eduf_lead` on `tbl_eduf_lead`.`id` = `tbl_client`.`eduf_id` left join `tbl_events` on `tbl_events`.`event_id` = `tbl_client`.`event_id` where `tbl_client_prog`.`status` = 1 and month(`success_date`) = '11' and year(`success_date`) = '2023' and
(CASE
WHEN tbl_client_prog.status = 0 THEN tbl_client_prog.created_at
WHEN tbl_client_prog.status = 1 THEN tbl_client_prog.success_date
WHEN tbl_client_prog.status = 2 THEN tbl_client_prog.failed_date
WHEN tbl_client_prog.status = 3 THEN tbl_client_prog.refund_date
END)
between '2023-11-01' and '2023-11-31' group by `lead_source`

select `cp_p`.`prog_id`, CONCAT(cp_mp.prog_name COLLATE utf8mb4_unicode_ci, ": ", cp_p.prog_program COLLATE utf8mb4_unicode_ci) as program_name_sales, (SELECT total_participant FROM tbl_sales_target WHERE tbl_sales_target.prog_id = cp_p.prog_id AND MONTH(month_year) = 11 AND YEAR(month_year) = 2023) as total_target_participant, (SELECT total_target FROM tbl_sales_target WHERE tbl_sales_target.prog_id = cp_p.prog_id AND MONTH(month_year) = 11 AND YEAR(month_year) = 2023) as total_target, (SELECT COUNT(*) FROM tbl_client_prog as q_cp WHERE q_cp.prog_id = cp_p.prog_id AND MONTH(q_cp.success_date) = 11 AND YEAR(q_cp.success_date) = 2023) as total_actual_participant, (SELECT SUM(q_i.inv_totalprice_idr) FROM tbl_client_prog as q_cp LEFT JOIN tbl_inv q_i ON q_i.clientprog_id = q_cp.clientprog_id WHERE q_cp.prog_id = cp_p.prog_id AND MONTH(q_cp.success_date) = 11 AND YEAR(q_cp.success_date) = 2023) as total_actual_amount from `tbl_client_prog` left join `tbl_inv` on `tbl_inv`.`clientprog_id` = `tbl_client_prog`.`clientprog_id` left join `tbl_prog` as `cp_p` on `cp_p`.`prog_id` = `tbl_client_prog`.`prog_id` left join `tbl_main_prog` as `cp_mp` on `cp_mp`.`id` = `cp_p`.`main_prog_id` left join `tbl_sales_target` on `tbl_sales_target`.`prog_id` = `cp_p`.`prog_id` where (month(`tbl_client_prog`.`success_date`) = '11' and year(`tbl_client_prog`.`success_date`) = '2023') or (month(`tbl_sales_target`.`month_year`) = '11' and year(`tbl_sales_target`.`month_year`) = '2023') group by `cp_p`.`prog_id`, CONCAT(cp_mp.prog_name, ": ", cp_p.prog_program)

select (CASE
WHEN tbl_lead.main_lead = "KOL" THEN CONCAT("KOL: ", tbl_lead.sub_lead)
WHEN tbl_lead.main_lead = "External Edufair" THEN (CASE WHEN tbl_eduf_lead.title != null THEN CONCAT(tbl_eduf_lead.title) ELSE (CASE WHEN tbl_eduf_lead.sch_id IS NULL THEN ceduf.corp_name ELSE seduf.sch_name END)END)
WHEN tbl_lead.main_lead = "All-In Partners" THEN CONCAT("All-In Partners: ", tbl_corp.corp_name)
ELSE tbl_lead.main_lead
END) AS conversion_lead, COUNT((CASE
WHEN tbl_lead.main_lead = "KOL" THEN CONCAT(tbl_lead.sub_lead)
WHEN tbl_lead.main_lead = "External Edufair" THEN (CASE WHEN tbl_eduf_lead.title != null THEN CONCAT(tbl_eduf_lead.title) ELSE (CASE WHEN tbl_eduf_lead.sch_id IS NULL THEN ceduf.corp_name ELSE seduf.sch_name END)END)
WHEN tbl_lead.main_lead = "All-In Partners" THEN CONCAT(tbl_corp.corp_name)
ELSE tbl_lead.main_lead
END)) AS count_conversionLead from `tbl_client_event` left join `tbl_lead` on `tbl_lead`.`lead_id` = `tbl_client_event`.`lead_id` left join `tbl_eduf_lead` on `tbl_eduf_lead`.`id` = `tbl_client_event`.`eduf_id` left join `tbl_corp` on `tbl_corp`.`corp_id` = `tbl_client_event`.`partner_id` left join `tbl_corp` as `ceduf` on `ceduf`.`corp_id` = `tbl_eduf_lead`.`corp_id` left join `tbl_sch` as `seduf` on `seduf`.`sch_id` = `tbl_eduf_lead`.`sch_id` group by `conversion_lead`

select (CASE
WHEN tbl_agenda_speaker.event_id is not null THEN tbl_events.event_title
WHEN tbl_agenda_speaker.eduf_id is not null THEN
(CASE
WHEN tbl_eduf_lead.title IS NOT NULL THEN tbl_eduf_lead.title
ELSE
(CASE
WHEN tbl_eduf_lead.sch_id is NULL THEN CONCAT(tbl_corp.corp_name, " (", DATE_FORMAT(tbl_eduf_lead.created_at, "%e %b %Y"), ")")
ELSE CONCAT(tbl_sch.sch_name, " (", DATE_FORMAT(tbl_eduf_lead.created_at, "%e %b %Y"), ")")
END)
END)
WHEN tbl_agenda_speaker.sch_prog_id > 0 OR tbl_agenda_speaker.partner_prog_id > 0
THEN
(CASE
WHEN tbl_prog.sub_prog_id > 0 THEN CONCAT(tbl_sub_prog.sub_prog_name," - ",tbl_prog.prog_program)
ELSE tbl_prog.prog_program
END)
END) AS event_name, (CASE
WHEN tbl_agenda_speaker.sch_pic_id > 0 THEN tbl_schdetail.schdetail_fullname
WHEN tbl_agenda_speaker.partner_pic_id > 0 THEN tbl_corp_pic.pic_name
WHEN tbl_agenda_speaker.univ_pic_id > 0 THEN tbl_univ_pic.name
WHEN tbl_agenda_speaker.empl_id > 0 THEN CONCAT(users.first_name," ",users.last_name)
ELSE null
END) AS speaker_name, `tbl_agenda_speaker`.`start_time`, `tbl_agenda_speaker`.`end_time` from `tbl_agenda_speaker` left join `tbl_sch_prog` on `tbl_agenda_speaker`.`sch_prog_id` = `tbl_sch_prog`.`id` left join `tbl_partner_prog` on `tbl_partner_prog`.`id` = `tbl_agenda_speaker`.`partner_prog_id` left join `tbl_prog` on `tbl_prog`.`prog_id` = CASE
WHEN tbl_agenda_speaker.sch_prog_id > 0 THEN
tbl_sch_prog.prog_id
WHEN tbl_agenda_speaker.partner_prog_id > 0 THEN
tbl_partner_prog.prog_id
ELSE null
END left join `tbl_sub_prog` on `tbl_sub_prog`.`id` = `tbl_prog`.`sub_prog_id` left join `tbl_events` on `tbl_events`.`event_id` = `tbl_agenda_speaker`.`event_id` left join `tbl_eduf_lead` on `tbl_eduf_lead`.`id` = `tbl_agenda_speaker`.`eduf_id` left join `tbl_corp` on `tbl_corp`.`corp_id` = `tbl_eduf_lead`.`corp_id` left join `tbl_sch` on `tbl_sch`.`sch_id` = `tbl_eduf_lead`.`sch_id` left join `tbl_schdetail` on `tbl_schdetail`.`schdetail_id` = `tbl_agenda_speaker`.`sch_pic_id` left join `tbl_univ_pic` on `tbl_univ_pic`.`id` = `tbl_agenda_speaker`.`univ_pic_id` left join `tbl_corp_pic` on `tbl_corp_pic`.`id` = `tbl_agenda_speaker`.`partner_pic_id` left join `users` on `users`.`id` = `tbl_agenda_speaker`.`empl_id` where `tbl_agenda_speaker`.`status` = 1

WHEN tbl_invb2b.partnerprog_id > 0 THEN tbl_partner_prog.status

WHEN tbl_receipt.invdtl_id is not null THEN
(CASE
WHEN tbl_invdtl.invb2b_id is not null THEN
(CASE
WHEN tbl_invb2b.schprog_id > 0 THEN tbl_sch_prog.status
WHEN tbl_invb2b.partnerprog_id > 0 THEN tbl_partner_prog.status
WHEN tbl_invb2b.ref_id > 0 THEN tbl_referral.referral_type
END)
WHEN tbl_invdtl.inv_id is not null THEN tbl_client_prog.status
END)
WHEN tbl_receipt.inv_id is not null THEN tbl_client_prog.status
WHEN tbl_invb2b.schprog_id is not null THEN tbl_sch_prog.status
WHEN tbl_invb2b.partnerprog_id is not null THEN tbl_partner_prog.status

WHEN b2b_p_p.prog_id IS NOT NULL THEN b2b_p_p.program_name

WHEN tbl_receipt.receipt_cat = "partner" THEN tbl_partner_prog.refund_date

WHEN tbl_receipt.receipt_cat = "partner" THEN tbl_partner_prog.id

WHEN tbl_receipt.receipt_cat = "partner" THEN "partner_prog"

WHEN tbl_receipt.receipt_cat = "partner" THEN tbl_invb2b.invb2b_id
